100
00:05:59.260 --> 00:06:02.604
SoIntestinal metaplasia is the

101
00:06:02.664 --> 00:06:06.564
conversion of gastric cell into intestinalized cells, and

102
00:06:07.004 --> 00:06:09.824
it is usually a consequence of chronic inflammation,

103
00:06:11.104 --> 00:06:14.704
and it has a wide prevalence, especially in

104
00:06:14.784 --> 00:06:18.404
Asian population. Histologically, it has been

105
00:06:18.444 --> 00:06:22.404
classified into the complete and incomplete type, and the incomplete

106
00:06:22.484 --> 00:06:26.444
type is said to be associated with a higher risk of gastric cancer

107
00:06:26.504 --> 00:06:30.284
conversion. However, study of this is

108
00:06:30.304 --> 00:06:34.284
limited because there is no representative sensitive 2D cell line model,

109
00:06:34.764 --> 00:06:38.084
and the animal model, especially in mice, only partially

110
00:06:38.484 --> 00:06:42.354
resemble human metaplasia. And mice

111
00:06:42.464 --> 00:06:46.304
mainly displace the so-called spam instead

112
00:06:46.364 --> 00:06:48.734
of true intestinal metaplasia.

113
00:06:49.704 --> 00:06:53.654
In collaboration with Mike Stratton in Sanger Institute, we have done

114
00:06:53.764 --> 00:06:54.364
a deep

115
00:06:55.344 --> 00:06:58.944
