116
00:06:59.004 --> 00:07:01.684
crypts in individual gland in the stomach.

117
00:07:02.884 --> 00:07:06.744
And through study of more than 200 whole genome

118
00:07:06.824 --> 00:07:08.744
sequence of individual glands,

119
00:07:09.844 --> 00:07:12.564
we observe the number of

120
00:07:12.684 --> 00:07:16.084
