123
00:07:24.144 --> 00:07:25.244
around 2,000

124
00:07:26.084 --> 00:07:29.364
SNV mutation in each of the gland in your stomach.

125
00:07:30.184 --> 00:07:33.804
But in some of the gastric cancer patient, we see

126
00:07:33.884 --> 00:07:37.004
